name: Maria Peter
description:
I like listening to music and i like swimming,camping,shopping,reading,and even dance too, because music is really part of my life and i can’t do without listening to music in a day. And my kind of music is Gospel R$B with Country and Opera.

I also like to hang out with my loved one as wellI like going to beach and cinema and i like playing basket ball and long tennis and swimming for fun, and i love all out doors games.
